112}},"width":1},"font":{"postscriptName":"Roboto-Medium","family":"Roboto","style":"Medium","size":18}},"text":{"frame":{"type":"area","width":1684,"height":269},"paragraphs":[{"lines":[[{"y":19,"from":0,"to":209,"x":0}],[{"y":43,"from":209,"to":286,"x":0}]]},{"lines":[[{"y":67,"from":287,"to":287,"x":0}]]},{"lines":[[{"y":91,"from":288,"to":492,"x":0}],[{"y":115,"from":492,"to":524,"x":0}]]},{"lines":[[{"y":139,"from":525,"to":525,"x":0}]]},{"lines":[[{"y":163,"from":526,"to":727,"x":0}]]},{"lines":[[{"y":187,"from":728,"to":728,"x":0}]]},{"lines":[[{"y":211,"from":729,"to":893,"x":0}]]}],"rawText":"Shared safari can only be created from profile but Fixed departure from pages. Fixed departure will have all the details along with creator's rating because page will have ratings and reviews. Fixed departure creator knows all the details along with price and does all the arrangements.\n\nShared safari by individual will be just an idea or proposal to other people with rough estimate of everything and can be changed depending on the discussion on the thread. There will be no details. Just discussion tab will be only tab.\n\nDifference between Fixed Departure and Package will be just the date. Fixed departure as name says, has fixed date and other itinerary. Whereas, package is offered for the season and can be customized.\n\nBoth Shared safari by individual and Fixed departure by Photographers and Influencers will be treated in Shared Safari because both will be shared unlike a Package."}},{"type":"group","name":"Group 5834","meta":{"ux":{"nameL10N":"SHAPE_GROUP","constraintLeft":true,"constraintWidth":true,"constraintTop":true,"constraintHeight":true,"localTransform":{"a":1,"b":0,"c":0,"d":1,"tx":645.29296875,"ty":348}}},"id":"e19413de-387d-45c2-b4d9-04b23a94a048","transform":{"a":1,"b":0,"c":0,"d":1,"tx":-9641.70703125,"ty":12236},"group":{"children":[{"type":"group","name":"Component 20 – 6","meta":{"ux":{"nameL10N":"SHAPE_COMPONENT","symbolOverrides":{"addedGuids":